HEADWORD: Water rocket
<hw>Wa"ter rock"et</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <sn>1.</sn> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>A cruciferous plant (<spn>Nasturtium sylvestre</spn>) with small
yellow flowers.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A kind of firework to be discharged in the
water.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Water-rot</ent>⟦br⟧
